{"tid":1173957,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓娛圈醜聞】楊賢碩被爆帶25名女性招呼富豪 警方指確認後才展開調查","createTime":"2019-05-27T13:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T00:24:51.000Z","uid":143093,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df85cb598e933a163f1f9eadfbc5dda30f5ab48b","tid":1173957,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ax0JY67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fax0JY67.jpg&h=13774cbf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n勝利（已入罪）和楊賢碩<br />\n<br />\n韓國天團BIGBANG前成員勝利捲入連串是非，當中包括性招待、性交易、貪污等，他已於3月宣佈退出娛樂圈，同時原本所屬的YG事務所亦宣佈與他解約。<br />\n而MBC節目《Straight》昨晚公開了以「追擊YG楊賢碩俱樂部性招待疑惑」為題的預告，由於勝利曾被爆利用YG信用卡付款予性招待的費用，雖然YG否認，但外界認為YG難以撇清關係。<br />\n節目於預告中爆料指YG老闆楊賢碩及韓流明星涉性招待了1名泰國富豪和1名馬來西亞富豪，目擊者指當日邀請8名男生和25名女性出席活動，當中該25名女性是與YG相熟的酒店小姐，眾人之後再到楊賢碩的夜店繼續玩樂。<br />\n對於爆出性招待，YG方面就否認，強調完全不是事實，又表示：「楊賢碩確實收到熟人邀請而出席活動，但從未進行過任何形式的招待。」而韓國警方今日下午表示，對於媒體爆料楊賢碩涉性招待一事，警方指目前仍未收到相關的報案，將在確認節目爆料後再決定是否展開調查。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，節目預告亦提到勝利有份投資的夜店Burning Sun曾涉泰國富豪強姦事件，並採訪當時的受害女性。節目將於今晚播出。</span><br />\n而事件爆出後，YG的股價亦於今天上午暴跌，雖然YG方面已第一時間已否認性招待傳聞，但其股價今日開市即大幅下跌9.3%，比上一個交易日暴跌13.26%，跌破了3萬韓圜（約198港元），創下了最近一年的新低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190527/59645495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F59645495&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=5c002e38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190527%2F59645495&h=c7d518e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190527/59645495</a><br />\n勝利sir叫雞咋！！邊有扯皮條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJurctj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJurctj.gif&h=e1a3d88c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d998d191aa3cc42ea1641c8f02100616223246ef","tid":1173957,"uid":213300,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"YG幾時收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c3ace441366191cba9901af9c54f4cd25aa625","tid":1173957,"uid":198730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"港女：勝利快啲強姦我"},{"pid":"d4d4fbaa614bc55826288ef3d557874e717d53c8","tid":1173957,"uid":240608,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"blackpink 有無比yg ,富豪訓過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22beb2232c8cbbdbd99cecda5d5e2a23af2a5f3d","tid":1173957,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"jisoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef26fe6a36978e0f6c91652db2f44e13c7877f6","tid":1173957,"uid":134171,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"Yg收皮之時 <br />\n就係我同牙秀成親嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d041e4f053c0342d644b28aa4f42c79ce7cec6b","tid":1173957,"uid":240608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"22beb2232c8cbbdbd99cecda5d5e2a23af2a5f3d","tid":1173957,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"jisoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c